{"id": 1006, "genre": 1001, "title": "你会如何有意识地保护自己的隐私？", "description": "一种谨慎的无奈。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 5058, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170322101549XI2cnwAQiJyY6LbP.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-25T11:02:32Z", "options": [{"id": 81924, "content": "不到不得已，不开启手机的地理位置可见功能。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622577}, {"id": 81925, "content": "买了阿里小号，在外面留号码都留这个号码", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 560296}, {"id": 82182, "content": "无痕浏览", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517018}, {"id": 81930, "content": " 笔记本摄像头贴粘纸！ 笔记本摄像头贴粘纸！ 笔记本摄像头贴粘纸！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622583}, {"id": 82698, "content": "烧掉所有pos单", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590525}, {"id": 81931, "content": "小孩要玩手机的时候设软件锁", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622140}, {"id": 81932, "content": "用了别人的电脑后，删除所有的历史记录", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622700}, {"id": 88844, "content": "手机包括能设密码的app都设密码", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643499}, {"id": 81933, "content": "不实名不认证不绑定手机号", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 559295}, {"id": 81935, "content": "将好友与同事、普通朋友分隔开来", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613984}, {"id": 81936, "content": "快递单如果是手写就喷花露水，是打印的就用黑笔涂或者直接撕碎碎的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 339656}, {"id": 81938, "content": "暂时不需要特别多的隐私", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602358}, {"id": 81939, "content": "快递个人信息撕碎", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 551266}, {"id": 81943, "content": "偶尔在社交网络发点混淆视听的信息( ˙˘˙ )", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622815}, {"id": 82199, "content": "不让好友知道我在网易云音乐里开了账号", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623494}, {"id": 81945, "content": "把片片用上帝模式隐藏掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622827}, {"id": 81946, "content": "无痕浏览", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594896}, {"id": 81948, "content": "沉默或者岔开话题 朋友圈分群组发送", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591523}, {"id": 81949, "content": "离开办公桌就锁屏、即使是一小会", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594949}, {"id": 81950, "content": "身份证复印件必须覆盖用途", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622855}, {"id": 81951, "content": "断开连接", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216033}, {"id": 82211, "content": "有人靠近的时候会举起手防御，防止被人撞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404804}, {"id": 83748, "content": "朋友圈删光了?大概已经属于过度保护了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630419}, {"id": 100644, "content": "網上不用真名，app拒絕被索取個人資料", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688332}, {"id": 82983, "content": "在群里面爆照之后会立刻撤回，即便有人存了也不会让其乱发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260080}, {"id": 83239, "content": "故意输错密码，让手机停机", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627805}, {"id": 81971, "content": "朋友圈分组特别详细却还是不发。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622880}, {"id": 81973, "content": "没有朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566873}, {"id": 81974, "content": "填快递地址只填到街道，不写门牌号", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622891}, {"id": 81975, "content": "尽量不在网络上发东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618827}, {"id": 81977, "content": "上厕所关门", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622893}, {"id": 81978, "content": "上厕所关门", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622893}, {"id": 81979, "content": "上厕所关门", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622893}, {"id": 81981, "content": "上厕所关门╮(╯▽╰)╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622893}, {"id": 81982, "content": "qq空间只有自己可见 个性签名是空白 朋友圈只发自拍➕表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622168}, {"id": 97599, "content": "不吃陌生人的棒棒糖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677431}, {"id": 81984, "content": "删除访客记录.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621777}, {"id": 81985, "content": "不带我玩儿？发不了？我去？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622893}, {"id": 81986, "content": "算了，不玩儿了，不好玩儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622893}, {"id": 81987, "content": "1.不连接陌生的不加密WIFI\n2.不点击不明来源链接\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622919}, {"id": 81988, "content": "软件锁开到自己都想摔手机了╮(￣⊿￣)╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615098}, {"id": 81989, "content": "1.不连陌生无密码WIFI\n2.朋友圈不允许陌生人，看私密动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622919}, {"id": 81990, "content": "拍证件照后 把电脑里自己的照片删掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249034}, {"id": 81991, "content": "发状态从不定位", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249034}, {"id": 81993, "content": "放在桌子上的个人信息甚至是作业都会翻过来反面朝上.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590948}, {"id": 96843, "content": "社交软件不加不认识的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671826}, {"id": 81996, "content": "闭上嘴巴不说话装作什么都不知道的样子藏起来做好自己", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182834LXUKOY8twkyJdA13", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450806}, {"id": 81997, "content": "藏起来做好自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450806}, {"id": 81998, "content": "正在浏览网页，过来个人探头来看，必然换一夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622952}, {"id": 84563, "content": "很少点微博好友圈的赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634003}]}